  already exists in auth.ts, and added an explicit per-table isolation
  checkpoint inside the read-swap prompt instead of only at the end.
- New tests for the Formspree submission (mocked fetch, since this
  environment has no network access to formspree.io or supabase.co to
  test against directly).
